Automated Radiology Report + Care Pathway:

Multi Agent, because multiple independent tasks can be executed simultaneously and later combined into a single final report.

---------------------------------------------------------
{Medical Scan Input}
        ↓
{Parallelly: Generate Diagnostic Report,
             Validate Patient History,
             Schedule Follow-up Appointment,
             Create Doctor & Patient Summary}
        ↓
{Consolidate Outputs}
        ↓
{Deliver Final Clinical Report}
