Multi Agent, because different diagnostic activities can be performed independently before deciding on corrective actions.

---------------------------------------------------------
{Alert Generated}
        ↓
{Parallelly: Monitor System Metrics,
             Analyze Application Logs,
             Verify Database Health}
        ↓
{Assess Root Cause}
